A real-life example of Azure Web Apps is an e-commerce website.

The frontend is hosted on Azure Web Apps, providing a responsive user interface.

For example, users can browse products, add items to cart, and place orders.

A real-life scenario is online shopping platforms handling thousands of users simultaneously.

Another example is a company website with dynamic content such as blogs and customer portals.

Web Apps ensure scalability, reliability, and ease of deployment.
